&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; information that can't be shared. I've created a public version of the
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; design document that you can access here:
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1CBH4r6rxSryY28hOhBQC-DZgjwWbO-FRYg_bbJIfBFo"&gt;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1CBH4r6rxSryY28hOhBQC-DZgjwWbO-FRYg_bbJIfBFo&lt;/a&gt;
