&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; On documentation: we have a PR up against Fetch at
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/whatwg/fetch/pull/1840"&gt;https://github.com/whatwg/fetch/pull/1840&lt;/a&gt; which aims to clarify the
