&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; other Chromium-based browsers. Web Platform behaviour differences 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; between
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; our implementations opens up risks of ongoing divergence, and so I'm 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; going
