&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; practice &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://www.chromium.org/developers/enterprise-changes/"&gt;https://www.chromium.org/developers/enterprise-changes/&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; for breaking changes that we predict may have enterprise impact.
