&gt;&gt; standards-positions/issues/1271)
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *WebKit*: No signal (&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt; standards-positions/issues/528)
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *Web developers*: Positive First-party partners at Google are excited to
&gt;&gt; be able associate specific app state &amp; data with web-exposed crash reports.
