&lt;pre&gt;Does this still need to be added to a spec? &quot;activeViewTransition&quot; doesn't 
appear anywhere in &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-view-transitions-2"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-view-transitions-2&lt;/a&gt; or 
at &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-document"&gt;https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-document&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

