&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/12407"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/12407&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;
&gt; *WebKit*: No signal (
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/536"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/536&lt;/a&gt;) Discussed at 
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/12407"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/12407&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;
&gt; *Web developers*: No signals
&gt;
&gt; *Other signals*:
&gt;
