&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Specification&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-content/#content-property"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-content/#content-property&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Summary
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; counter() and counters() in alt text of 'content' property is useful to 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; provide more meaningful information to e.g. pseudo elements to improve 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; their accessibility.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Blink componentBlink&gt;CSS 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3ECSS%22"&gt;https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3ECSS%22&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
