&gt; Yes, the I2S proposes using the system accent color when the value is set 
&gt; to &quot;auto&quot;. To clarify, &quot;auto&quot; is also the default option if no value is 
&gt; provided. Therefore, if the accent-color is not explicitly set, the form 
&gt; elements will automatically use the system accent color by default.
