&gt; viewport-segments 
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-viewport-1/#segments"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-viewport-1/#segments&lt;/a&gt;
&gt; *&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-env-1/#viewport-segments"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-env-1/#viewport-segments&lt;/a&gt; 
&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-env-1/#viewport-segments"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-env-1/#viewport-segments&lt;/a&gt;&gt;*
