&gt;
&gt; *WebKit*: No signal (&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/&lt;/a&gt;
&gt; standards-positions/issues/327)
&gt;
&gt; *Web developers*: Positive (&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://twitter.com/DanB/"&gt;https://twitter.com/DanB/&lt;/a&gt;
&gt; status/1179937850286059520) Another example: &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://twitter.com/"&gt;https://twitter.com/&lt;/a&gt;
