&gt;&gt; Link to entry on the Chrome Platform Status
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/feature/6494349985841152?gate=5122129510268928"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/feature/6494349985841152?gate=5122129510268928&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Links to previous Intent discussions
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Intent to Prototype:
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/g/blink-dev/c/Ie46tc6_8so/m/eY1huFmOAAAJ"&gt;https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/g/blink-dev/c/Ie46tc6_8so/m/eY1huFmOAAAJ&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Intent to Experiment:
